                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿يَنقَلِبَ﴾: يَرْجِعَ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿بُورٗا﴾: هَلْكَى.</h2>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
